        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Something speaks to you from beyond the stars or below the earth. Ancient and unknowable, this alien influence presses against your mind.</p>\n<p><strong>Spell List</strong> occult</p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Skills</strong> Intimidation, Occultism</p>\n<p><strong>Granted Spells</strong> cantrip <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Daze]</em>, 1st: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Spider Sting]</em>, 2nd: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Stupefy]{Touch of Idiocy}</em>, 3rd: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Vampiric Feast]{Vampiric Touch}</em>, 4th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Confusion]</em>, 5th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Black Tentacles]</em>, 6th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Never Mind]{Feeblemind}</em>, 7th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Warp Mind]</em>, 8th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Uncontrollable Dance]</em>, 9th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Spirit Song]</em></p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Spells</strong> initial: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Tentacular Limbs]</em>, advanced: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Aberrant Whispers]</em>, greater: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Unusual Anatomy]</em></p>\n<p><strong>Blood Magic</strong> Aberrant whispers shield one target's mind or your own, granting a +2 status bonus to Will saving throws for 1 round.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feat-effects.Item.Effect: Aberrant Blood Magic]</p>"
